  [Text] A new umbrella group of political parties, 
comprising parties from the socialist and Lumumbist paths, has 
just been set up in Zaire. It is called the Union of Congolese 
Leftists [Union de la Gauche Congolaise]. 
  According to lawyer Mukenge Ndibu, one of the creators of 
the 
movement, the left has an inactive military wing that can be 
easily mobilized with moral strength and an interest that only 
needs to be awakened, end quote. [no reference to opening 
quotation as heard] 

