<H3> <TI>   Wei Jianxing, Delegation Return From Middle East </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Wei Jianxing, Delegation Return From Middle East </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2905131194 Beijing XINHUA in English 1236 GMT 29 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2905131194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, May 29 (XINHUA) -- The delegation from the 
Communist Party of China (CPC) headed by Wei Jianxing, member of 
the Political Bureau and also member of the Secretariat of the 
CPC Central Committee, wound up its official goodwill visit to 
Egypt and Syria and returned here today. 
  The delegation was met at the airport by Li Shuzheng, head 
of 
the International Liaison Department of the CPC Central 
Committee, and embassy officials of the above two countries in 
Beijing. 

</TEXT>

