<H3> <TI>   Filming of TV Series on National Defense Completed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Filming of TV Series on National Defense Completed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW3105042994 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0823 
GMT 27 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW3105042994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By reporters Zhang Min (1728 2404) and He Guanggao (6320 </F>
0342 7559)] 
  [Text] Beijing, 27 May (XINHUA) -- A television film "The 
Great Wall Is in My Heart" -- a joint production of the 
Mobilization Department of the General Staff Headquarters and 
the Mass Work Department of the General Political Department -- 
whose title was inscribed by Jiang Zemin, has been completed. 
The eight-part defense education series will soon be 
distributed to people's armed forces departments across the 
nation. 
  "The Great Wall Is in My Heart" is China's first 
comprehensive and systematic educational TV film on national 
defense. Guided by the basic tenets of Marxism-Leninism-Mao 
Zedong Thought and based on Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory on 
building socialism with Chinese characteristics and his ideas on 
army building in the new period, the series employs a large 
amount of stirring historical data and illustrative facts in 
presenting a vivid picture of how the three generations of CPC 
leadership collectives care about and value defense buildup. 
The series, which gives publicity to the series of principles 
and policies for China's national defense buildup; the 
achievements scored in this regard; and national defense laws 
and regulations including the "Military Service Law"; and 
disseminates modern defense knowledge, is visual teaching 
material on defense education for the broad mass of militiamen, 
reservists, and youngsters. 

</TEXT>

