Affairs Minister Fang Chin-yen and his wife, Economic Affairs 
Minister P. K. Chiang, Council of Agriculture Chairman Sun Ming- 
hsien and Government Information Office Director-General Jason 
Hu. 
  Lien and his party will return on June 7. 

