  [Text] Los Angeles, May 29 (CNA) -- Premier Lien Chan 
arrived in Los Angeles Sunday [29 May] afternoon for an 
overnight stay on his way to Central America for a state visit. 
  Lien was met at the airport by Natale Bellocchi, managing 
